                <head>The Maryland Election</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Mourns the loss of the "freedom of the ballot" in Maryland, where no "real"
                    election has been held in the last three years. The editor says that the
                    elections that have been held have been fraudulent since voters have been
                    required to take loyalty oaths.</summary>
                <note/>
